<% content_for(:page_title, t('service.title', page_title: 'Confirmation')) %>
<% content_for(:page_name, 'Nudge Booking Confirmation') %>
<% content_for(:tool_step, '3') %>


<div class="l-grid-row">
  <div class="l-column-two-thirds">
    <div class="govuk-box-highlight">
      <h2>Your Pension Wise appointment is confirmed</h2>

      <div class="t-start">
        <p><strong>Date</strong><br><%= l(@booking_date, format: :govuk_date) %></p>
        <p><strong>Time</strong><br><%= l(@booking_date, format: :govuk_time) %> (<%= current_timezone(@booking_date) %>)</p>
        <p><strong>Reference number</strong><br><span class="t-booking-reference"><%= @booking_reference %></span></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p>You should receive a booking confirmation, including how best to prepare for your appointment.</p>
    <p>Remember, Pension Wise cannot speak to you if you’re driving – even if you use a hands-free device.</p>

    <h3>How to change your appointment</h3>
    <p>To change your Pension Wise appointment or any information you’ve given us, call <strong>0800 100 166</strong>.</p>

    <h3>How to cancel your appointment</h3>
    <p>You can cancel your appointment online at <a href="https://www.moneyhelper.org.uk/en/pensions-and-retirement/pension-wise/book-a-free-pension-wise-appointment/cancel-pension-wise-appointment" target="_blank">moneyhelper.org.uk/cancel-pension-wise-phone</a> or by replying to your booking confirmation.</p>

    <h3>How to prepare for your appointment</h3>
    <p>You’ll usually benefit more if you:</p>

    <ul>
      <li>Ask each pension provider:
        <ul>
          <li>how much your pension is currently worth</li>
          <li>if your pension has any special features, like a guaranteed pot value or annuity rate.</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>Check your State Pension forecast:
        <ul>
          <li>at <strong>gov.uk/check-state-pension</strong> or</li>
          <li>call <strong>0800 731 0175</strong> between 8am and 6pm, Monday to Friday.</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>Have details of your other finances, like:
        <ul>
          <li>savings and investments</li>
          <li>debts and repayments.</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>Think about your plan for retirement, such as:
        <ul>
          <li>when you’d like to stop working</li>
          <li>what type of pension income you’d like.</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p>For more information, see your booking confirmation or go to <a href="https://www.moneyhelper.org.uk/prepare-pw" target="_blank">moneyhelper.org.uk/prepare-pw</a>.</p>
  </div>
</div>
